[ch [title Introduction]

    The [i Practical Data and Markup Language] (PDML) is a text format to store data.

    A distinction is made between [i Basic PDML] and [i PDML Extensions]. [i Basic PDML] is the minimum needed to store data. Extensions are optional features to make PDML more practical.
    
    This document is the official specification for [i Basic PDML].
]
